description: GET READY TO SWAP ‘TIL YA DROP! In this episode, Lisa dishes out the 6 swaps you MUST HAVE, plus her swap of the week (maybe of the year)! Here’s a hint, it’s a vegetable, but it’s not cauliflower! And our very first CHEW & TELL featuring 3 TRADER JOE’s swap finds!
